<P>A <HI>COMEDY,</HI> IN FIVE ACTS.</P>
<P>PERFORMED AT THE LONDON AND DUBLIN THEATRES WITH UNIVERSAL APPLAUSE&mdash;AND AT GREENWICH-STREET, N. YORK.</P>
