<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mi&s;s <HI>Dor</HI></SPEAKER>
<P><HI>(catching hold of him&punc;)</HI> For once I give up my pride to &s;often yours. Come, do not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">ook thus determined?&mdash;I am &s;ure Mr&punc; Mandred did not mean to offend me; the words he made u&s;e of fell from his lips by accident.</P>
