</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Bronzely.</SPEAKER>
<P>Thus invited, encouraged to &s;peak, I will &s;peak boldly&mdash;and I can heaven to witne&s;s, that what I am going to &s;a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady <HI>Priory.</HI></SPEAKER>
